<i>noun</i>: 휴정 [휴정], 정회 [정회/정훼] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>휴정 [휴정]</dt><br>
<dd>adjournment; recess</dd><br>
<dd>법원에서, 재판을 잠시 쉬는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of taking a brief break in a court trial.</dd><br>
<dt>정회 [정회/정훼]</dt><br>
<dd>1. adjournment</dd><br>
<dd>회의 중에 회의를 잠시 멈춤.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of stopping a meeting for a short while.</dd><br>
<dd>2. adjournment</dd><br>
<dd>국회의 개회 중에 잠시 그 활동을 멈춤.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of stopping a congressional meeting for a short period of time while it is in session.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>